sample_comments.negatives:
Although we loved our stay, there are some small things that could have been better:
- guests should not be allowed to bring speakers and listen to their loud music on the beach, it was really disturbing, it should be a policy against that;
- the bathroom door should be fully closed from the ceiling to the ground, not as it is now, being an open bathroom with glass door makes it a bit disturbing to feel comfortable in the bathroom;
- waiters should come at least some times during the day to the beach to take orders, I know the beach bar is only some minutes away, but it is comfortable when you are relaxing at the beach to be able to order drinks;
- the food at the Mad Cow restaurant is very expensive, even though is very good, it's still very overpriced, we've been for one month to top hotels in Vietnam and we know the prices;
- please don't put the toiletries in the "anti-theft" system in the bathrooms, it makes it difficult to use them since they are blocked there, use small toiletries instead of using those blocking systems for the bottles.
